programme.desc: Sebuah program bual bicara santai selebriti yang menampilkan barisan artis terkenal di setiap episod. Di hoskan oleh Ajak, Huru Hara kali ini pasti membuatkan anda terhibur sambil bergelak ketawa. Dalam episode ini saksikan Hilmy Ashley, Afieq Shazwan, Anas Ridzuan & Despanik.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep08
programme.desc: Memaparkan Hani menemani Sheila yang sakit hendak bersalin. Sheila memarahi dan meminta Hani tidak perlu menemainya. Hani sabar, tenang sebaliknya memaklumkan dia berbuat demikian atas kehendak ibu dan bapa mertua mereka. Setelah Hani menasihatinya dan meminta Sheila banyak istigfar dan berdoa daripada mengeluh dan ingat yang bukan-bukan, Sheila akhirnya berubah positif terhadap Hani. Nizam yang dihubungi Hani tidak menjawab. Sheila selamat melahirkan anaknya dan dia kekurangan darah dan Hani telah mendermanya. Mizan pula dimaklumkan Khalid tentang wanita idamannya tidak kelihatan beberapa hari. Jadi rancangan untuk menemuinya ditangguhkan dahulu. Sebelum itu Khalid juga bertanyakan Yusri tentang Hani tetapi Yusri juga tidak ketahui. Hani yang menjagai adik iparnya juga membantu ibu mentuanya di rumah. Dia keletihan dan ibunya meminta dia berehat dan tidur awal. Mizan pula mengutamakan ke kampungnya daripada majlis jemputan tetapi tiba lewat malam, Hani telah nyenyak tidur. Sheila berkali-kali menghantar pesanan ringkas kepada Nizam tetapi tiada sebarang jawapan. Dia juga teringat kisah lalu bagaimana bekas rakan lelakinya yang tidak mahu bertanggungjawab dan kemudiannya bertemu dengan Nizam.

programme.title: Pengantinku Jatuh Dari Langit S1 Ep22
programme.desc: Rinieta terkejut apabila mendapati Arfy tidur disebelahnya. Arfy minta izin untuk tidur bersama Rinieta kerana takut kononnya lembaga dikatakan hantu yang menghuni katilnya sepanjang percutian mereka sebelum ini menganggunya. Rinieta pula panik dan takut apabila melihat kegatalan Arfy semakin menjadi-jadi.

programme.title: Jangan Benci Cintaku S1 Ep15
programme.desc: Shah cuba memujuk Husna sebab Natisa masuk hospital. Husna betul betul nekad ingin berpisah dengan Shah akibat terlalu sakit hati, dipermainkan. Husna pula kini balik bercuti lama di kampung bersama ibunya dia nekad untuk memulakan hidup baru. Shah masih sukar menerima hakikat. Hidangan sedap Feka sediakan semasa makan malam ditinggalkan begitu sahaja, malah dia tidur berasingan alasan nak tengok bola apabila Feka menyebut nama Husna. Sedang Faris dan Damia sedang merancang untuk membantu hubungan Feka/Shah, tiba tampil Shah terus menasihati mereka agar jangan masuk campur urusan dia. Agak memeranjat juga, tiba-tiba ibu Husna meminta Shah datang juga ke rumahnya. Lebih mengejutkan lagi Shah akui yang dia tidak lama lagi akan mengahwini Husna.

programme.title: Halalkan Hati Yang Ku Curi S1 Ep21
programme.desc: Faiq bekerja sebagai penjaga keselamatan. Sementara itu, dengan kerjasama imam, mereka kini telah menyewa sebuah rumah kayu yang kecil. Hubungan antara Tan Sri dengan isterinya, semakin baik, Tan Sri akui serta mengambil iktibar kesilapannya. Salima dilihat sering mengalah, ibunya sedar terutama dia tahu tindak tanduk Zainal. Puan Sri berpakat untuk tindakan drastik untuk "mengajar"nya kembali. Mereka akan membuka pekungnya semasa sambutan Hari Jadi Salima nanti. Delisha tidak dapat bekerja sebagai pencuci lagi, Faiq rela isterinya tinggal di rumah, kebetulan dia berdampingan Kak Anum, isteri Imam membantu buat kuih tempahan. Kemudiannya Delisha mengikut Kak Anum menghantar kuih di rumah Puan Sri Azman. Semasa Kak Anum mengulas perangai buruk Salima, Delisha tidak segan silu akui dulunya dia juga berperangai sebegitu. Delisha juga memaklumkan dia kenal Salima. Keesokannya, Delisha tidak sihat dan tidak lalu makan. Kak Anum membawanya ke hospital, doktor mengesahkan Delisha mengandung sebulan.

programme.title: Permainan Cinta S1 Ep03
programme.desc: Syifa dan Safiah menyamar sebagai wartawan untuk meninjau keadaan cara bekerja di makmal Dr Arman. Mereka juga bertemu dengan rakan sekerja Dr.Arman iaitu Dr Soraya, sambil mereka meninjau makmal dan selesai mengintip mereka dapat idea bagaimana hendakmasuk ke makmal Dr. Arman. Di sebabkan mereka bersaing mereka beraing mereka rahsiakan rancangan masing masing. Langkah pertama mereka berjumpa dengan Tukai,pakar membuat kad pengenalan palsu dan segala jnis dokumen rasmi. Syifa menyamar sebagai pelajar universiti yang ingin buat praktikal dan Safiah sebagai kerani am

programme.title: Permainan Cinta S1 Ep04
programme.desc: Dr Soraya curiga dengan tingah laku Safiah dan menyoal Safiah kerana masuk ke bilik Dr. Arman. Dr Soraya marahkan Safiah kerana masuk ke tempat yang tidak sepatutnya.Syifa cuba dekatkan diri dengan Dr Arman. Dia tahu Dr Arman berasal dari Kedah dan Syifa ci[ta satu persona@penyamaran sebagai gadis kampung dari Kedah, namun cara itu tidak membuahkan hasil. Ketika Dr Arman sibuk di makmal, Syifa cuba pikat dengan masakan nya. Dr Soraya sedar Dr.Arman semakin rapat dengan Syifa dan Safiah, dia telah sengaja buli mereka dan malukan mereka di depan Dr Arman. Syifa dan Safiah mula berpakat untuk kena kan Dr.Soraya depan semua staff.

programme.title: Jom Kahwin Ep09
programme.desc: Walaupun Jalal dan Salman menunjukkan pelbagai bukti, Adam tetap tidak percaya dengan tuduhan mereka yang Fatiha sebenarnya berniat buruk pada Adam sekeluarga. Salman menghalang Adam dari pulang dan mengurungnya. Chad pula semakin tidak senang dengan sikap Hajar yang suka berhujah, berleter serta sering memperkecilkan dirinya. Fatiha semakin risau apabila mendapat tahu yang Adam ada bersama Jalal. Bimbang rahsianya terbongkar, Fatiha segera ke rumah Jalal, sebelum terlambat…

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep09
programme.desc: Memaparkan Hani semasa berada di kampung bukan sahaja menjaga Sheila dan anaknya, tetapi menguruskan rumah tangga bersama ibunya. Di hujung minggu Mizan juga pulang. Mizan menunjukkan hubungan dia dengan Hani mesra. Hani secara ikhlas juga menunjukkan mesranya mereka berdua. Walau pun begitu mereka tidak sempat bersama sebagai suami isteri, bererti sejak mereka berkahwin masih berkeadaan sedemikian kerana di Kuala Lumpur pun mereka tinggal di bilik berasingan. Kesempatan Mizan dapat berbual ringkas dengan Hani, Mizan memberi amaran kepada Hani supaya sentiasa menunjukkanhubungan mereka kepada kedua-dua ibu bapa sebagai tidak ada masalah apa-apa pun. Hani akur, Kebetulan anak Sheila tidak sihat membuatkan semasa Mizan hendak pulang ke Kuala Lumpur, Hani tidak turut serta. Semasa Mizan hendak pulang, kedua-dua mereka "beraksi", pura-pura baik dan mesra kerana ibu dan bapa mereka ada bersama. Sheila kini bukan sahaja berterima kasih kepada Sheila tetapi dia juga menceritakan Nizam seorang yang baik, sanggup menerimanya. Dia juga menanti Nizam dengan penuh mengharap menerimanya. Selain itu menyatakan ibu dan bapanya mungkin akan bertambah marah apabila dapat tahu dia telah melahirkan anak. Mizan selepas tiba di Kuala Lumpur kelihatan kurang ceria dan menjadi kehairanan kepada Zul.

programme.desc: Memaparkan Sheila dan Nizam melawat Hani di hospital akibat keguguran. Di perkarangan hospital, Nizam meminta Sheila masuk dahulu. Ketika inilah Nizam diugut oleh lelaki upahan Suraya. Hubungan Nizam dan Sheila masih tegang dan dingin.. Seterusnya Nizam memaksa dan ugut Suraya agar mengaku angkara ugutan diupahnya, malahan meminta Suraya akui juga anaknya itu anak luar nikah. Suraya sekadar menidakkan dan Nizam masih bekeras. Tatkala ibu, bapa, Mizan, Hani dan turut ada Nizam berbincang di mana ibu mereka berharap Hani berpantang dan terus tinggal di rumah Sheila dan Mizan pula belum pulih, Nizam amat menyokong. Sebaliknya Hani dan Mizan tidak setuju membuatkan perasaan Nizam marah, lebih-lebih lagi hubungan Hani dan Mizan semakin mesra dan saling sayang menyayangi. Dengan sedikit ruang Nizam bertemu Hani terus menagih kasih Hani. Sambil itu menyindir Hani yang sebegitu mesra dengan Mizan.. Secara berhemah Datin Umairah menangguh projek Dato Fuad dan meminta Shariff menyiasat teliti. Sementara itu Datin Umairah sedang dan akan membantu Shariff tentang hasrat Shariff terhadap Hani. Cuma Shariff diminta bersabar kerana selain Datin Umairah berharap ujian DNA dapat dibuat, dia sendiri akan menyiasat kerana diyakini Hani adik kandung Shariff. Mizan kini amat menyayangi Hani berharap Hani ke pejabatnya untuk menyemak jawatan yang dipohonnya, seterusnya dapat bekerja dibawah penyeliaan Datin Umairah.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep22
programme.desc: Memaparkan hubungan Mizan dan Hani terus begitu mesra dan mereka juga berbincang tentang kerjaya Hani dan Mizan berharap dia dapat mengikutnya ke pejabat untuk menyemak permohonan jawatannya yang ditemuduga oleh Shariff tempuh hari. Sebaliknya hubungan Nizam dan Sheila masih dingin sering tidak sehaluan. Ketika Hani ditemu bual lanjut oleh Datin Umairah, Mizan bertemu Shariff dipejabatnya, mereka berbual biasa berhubung punca kecederaan berlaku. Datin Umairah memutuskan akan memilih Hani, tetapi akan dimaklumkan kemudian. Sebaik-baik Hani beredar bersama Mizan, Shariff menemui Datin Umairah. Bagi Shariff dia sangat mengharapkan sesuatu yang posotif hasratnya terhadap Hani, sebaliknya Shariff disuruh terus menumpukan siasat projek yang bermasalah berpunca suaminya, Dato Fuad. Malahan Datin Umairah menegaskan Hani 90% adik kandungnya. Shariff kemudiannya perolehi pengesahan bahawa Suraya sering berdampingan dengan Dato Fuad. Sementara itu Suraya bersama Dato Fuad akan mengatur tindakan yang lebih agresif yang akan dihadapi NIzam kerana dia terus mengugut semula Suraya.

programme.title: Dia Menantu Rahsia Ep21
programme.desc: Memaparkan puan Sarah dimasukkan ke wad tetapi tidak kritikal. Hanya keluarga terdekat boleh melawat, jadi Engku Razi dan Kamelia serta Melissa yang turut ada, hanya menunggu di luar. Razi ingin menghantar balik tetapi Syakir berjanji akan hantarnya. Razi juga menawar kerja di pejabatnya kepada Melissa, tetapi Melissa menolak. Syakir ambil keputusan akan berada di samping ibunya. Syakir berjanji akan penuh tumpu menjaga puan Sarah yang boleh berbual tetapi lemah. Razi ambil peluang hantar Melissa, kesempatan itu Razi sekali lagi menyampaikan hasratnya. Melissa menolak dengan baik. Melissa berharap kini dia perlu kuat, kerana Syakir menumpukan kepada ibunya. Keesokan pagi, tuan Suhaimi datang, Syakir balik ke rumah bertemu Melissa. Apabila Kamelia datang, dia syorkan Melissa yang patut berada sepanjang masa mengawasinya. Puan Sarah setuju. Melissa mula menjaga baik puan Sarah tetapi ada sahaja yang tidak kena pada Melissa. Sempat juga mengutuk "kampung" kepada Melissa. Sementara itu hubungan Zamer dan ibunya menjadi dingin, Zamer anggapkan ibunya gagal meminang Melissa sejak awal lagi. Zamer mengancam tidak mahu berhubung dengan ibunya lagi. Emosi Zamer mempengaruhi tingkah lakunya. Dibiliknya, Zamer melekatkan beberapa gambar Melissa. Ada di antara gambar Melissa dicucuk, sambil bercakap seorang diri "begitulah rasa sakit, sedangkan hati ini lebih rasa sakit". Ibu Zamer di kampung akibat terasa marah kepada Melissa, lalu membawa mulut tentang Melissa yang telah berkahwin itu mungkin berlaku hubungan dengan suaminya yang tidak baik, berkahwin tetapi tidak dihebahkan. Ibu Melissa yang dapat tahu dari iparnya, agak bimbang tetapi bersabar. Memandangkan Syakir mendapati abangnya kurang sihat, dia ingin meneruskan jaga ibunya di sebelah malam. Pun begitu, puan Sarah mahukan Melissa mengawasinya siang dan malam. Syakir merayu kepada ibunya, tetapi gagal. Sementara itu Kamelia berubah perangai, kali ini dia ingin mendekati semula Syakir dan akan menggodanya, ibunya melarang tetapi dia tidak peduli. Sedangkan tuan Suhaimi juga memaklumkan kepada anak dan menantunya, yang ibu mereka ada masalah jantung, tetapi dia tidak boleh lupakan ego dan kehendaknya. Timbul rasa tuan Suhaimi agar mereka juga ikut dengan kehendaknya yang mahukan Syakir berkahwin dengan pilihannya. Syakir sesekali meminta Melissa tinggalkan sebentar ibunya, membuat Melissa jadi serba salah.

programme.title: Dia Menantu Rahsia Ep22
programme.desc: Memaparkan di sebelah malam Syakir datang dan meminta Melissa bertemunya di luar wad, Melissa agak bimbang tetapi keluar bertemu juga. Mereka sempat bergurau senda, mujur masa itu puan Sarah sedang tidur. Sesekali Syakir juga berbual dengan Jenny tentang perkembangannya. Nasihat Jenny secepat mungkin ibunya kena tahu juga. Sementara itu puan Sarah dibenar pulang dengan doktor menasihatnya, banyak rehat, jangan cepat marah dan makan ubat. Di rumahnya, puan Sarah mahukan Melissa terus menjaganya,.tuan Suhaimi ingin dapatkan ?nurse?, tetapi puan Sarah akui, setakat ini Melissa dapat menjaga baik semasa di hospital. Melissa tiada pilihan, begitu juga Syakir walau pun dia tidak suka..Dalam pada itu, Razi dan Kamelia terus berbincang dengan hasrat masing-masing, Kamelia masih mengatakan abangnya kurang berusaha. Manakala di kampung Melissa, ibu Zamer terus membuka cerita Melissa dah kahwin dengan orang kaya dari bandar dan tidak buat kenduri. Sedangkan Zamer anaknya kini merajuk. Terkini ibu Zamer tidak dapat menghubungi Zamer lagi, kerana Zamer menukar number. Sementara itu Zamer yang memandu membawa kamelia ke rumah Syakir tahu akan hasrat Kamelia dan dia menyokong penuh. Suatu hari, Syakir terkejut Kamelia berada di rumahnya dan siapkan makanan untuknya dan memaklumkan ibunya yang memberi kunci rumah. Puan Sarah seolaholah mendera Melissa, mutakhir dia menumpahkan air kopi panas ke tangan Melissa. Melissa hanya sabar. Syakir yang tahu mengadu kepada bapanya, bapanya berjanji akan mmujuk ibunya. Melissa kerap melawat puan Sarah, kebetulan Syakir ada, ada kalanya Melisa diminta keluar bilik, tetapi puan sarah mahukan Syakir dan Melissa bersama-sama ada di sampingnya. Syakir tidak senang, tetapi tidak terdaya. Syakir pula terpaksa menghantar Kamelia. Tatkala masa yang lapang lewat tengah malam, Syakir bertemu Melissa lebih secara mencuri bagi masing menghilang rindu walaupun sebentar sahaja. Suatu pagi, kamelia daang seperti biasa, sempat tuan Suhaimi menemuinya. Berikutan tuan Suhaimi berterus terang pendirian Syakir, mengesyor Kamelia jangan lagi berharap. Berikutan kamelia mengadu kepada Puan Sarah, berlaku ketegangan antara puan Sarah dengan suami. Puan Sarah masih berdegil, sebaik Melissa masuk untuk membawa sarapan, puan Melissa disergah sebagai mangsa. Berikutan itu, Melissa lemah badan dan pitam. Syakir membawa balik ke rumahnya (berpesan kepada Nora hantar ke rumahnya dengan beri cuti 3 hari). Di rumah Syakir menjaga baik Melissa.

programme.title: Halalkan Hati Yang Ku Curi S1 Ep21
programme.desc: Faiq bekerja sebagai penjaga keselamatan. Sementara itu, dengan kerjasama imam, mereka kini telah menyewa sebuah rumah kayu yang kecil. Hubungan antara Tan Sri dengan isterinya, semakin baik, Tan Sri akui serta mengambil iktibar kesilapannya. Salima dilihat sering mengalah, ibunya sedar terutama dia tahu tindak tanduk Zainal. Puan Sri berpakat untuk tindakan drastik untuk "mengajar"nya kembali. Mereka akan membuka pekungnya semasa sambutan Hari Jadi Salima nanti. Delisha tidak dapat bekerja sebagai pencuci lagi, Faiq rela isterinya tinggal di rumah, kebetulan dia berdampingan Kak Anum, isteri Imam membantu buat kuih tempahan. Kemudiannya Delisha mengikut Kak Anum menghantar kuih di rumah Puan Sri Azman. Semasa Kak Anum mengulas perangai buruk Salima, Delisha tidak segan silu akui dulunya dia juga berperangai sebegitu. Delisha juga memaklumkan dia kenal Salima. Keesokannya, Delisha tidak sihat dan tidak lalu makan. Kak Anum membawanya ke hospital, doktor mengesahkan Delisha mengandung sebulan.

programme.title: 1, 2 Bakar S3 Ep09
programme.desc: Episod ke-9 ini memaparkan Chef Anis Nabila, dibantu oleh artis jemputan Lana Nodin, mendemonstrasikan cara membuat Kuih Bakar, Naan Cheese With Prawn Masala dan Steam Bake Otak-Otak. Dipaparkan juga resepi pembuatan hidangan-hidangan tersebut.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep10
programme.desc: Memaparkan Sheila sangat mengharapkan Hani dapat berhubung dengan Nizam kerana Hani sahaja yang akan dilayan panggilan. Hani menelefon Nizam semata-mata kerana harapan Sheila, merayu dia pulang. Sheila berharap dia dapat meminta maaf akibat kesalahannya. Kesempatan Hani berbual, Nizam sering memujuk Hani, menyuarakan segala perasaan dan janji mereka dahulu. Malahan Mizan dengan berkeras hati menyatakan cintanya hanya Hani, bagi Sheila dia tidak sesekali akan memaafkannya. Apabila Hani menyatakan kesetiaan hanyalah kepada suaminya. Nizam sekali lagi bertegas yang dia akan menentukan Mizan tidak menyentuhnya. Hani walau pun seperti berbelah bagi, tetapi dia seorang yang cekal dan tetap taat kepada suaminya. Di sebelah malamnya, Hani terbawa-bawa bagaimana kisah mereka berdua bercinta dahulu. Malahan di satu taman, pernah mereka sama-sama meletakkan "kunci cinta" mereka sebagai janji seia sekata. Suraya masih dengan rakan lelaki yang cuba mencari kerja untuk dia menjadi "modelling". Apa pun melalui jalan pintas Suraya juga bersetuju menjadi pelacur berkelas melalui seorang ahli perniagaan berbangsa Cina. Mizan tidak berapa sihat, kebetulan Hani telah pulang ke rumah. Hani menjagai Mizan dengan sebaiknya. Mizan juga mahukan Hani memanggil dirinya "abang", yang menjadi Hani terasa berlainan. Mereka juga mula keluar bersekali bersantai.

programme.title: Lurah Dendam
programme.desc: Semasa dalam penerbangan ujian, serangan kecelakaan dan kumpulan parachuters, yang diketuai oleh Kapten Hanafi tidak lama lagi mendapati diri mereka terdampar di tengah-tengah mana-mana, jauh dari tamadun. Salah seorang ahli pasukan, Ivy hilang dan apabila satu-satunya jejak mereka didapati adalah pakaiannya, ketegangan muncul di kalangan kumpulan itu. Ramai yang menyalahkan Kapten Hanafi untuk kemalangan itu. Dalam pencarian mereka untuk Ivy, kumpulan itu tersandung pada misteri di dalam hutan. Tidak lama peristiwa-peristiwa aneh berlaku dan salah satu daripada mereka hilang. Adakah mereka dapat bertahan di bawah keadaan-keadaan yang mencabar ini dan mendapatkan akar misteri? Atau bolehkah pengkhianatan dan membalas dendam menjadi penyebabnya?

programme.title: Lampor: Keranda Terbang
programme.desc: Edwin dan Netta bersama dua anak mereka, Agam dan Sekar, kembali ke kampung Netta di Temanggung. Kampung yang telah ditinggal Netta 25 tahun bersama ibunya yang marah akan perbuatan sesat ayahnya. Netta harus menyampaikan pesan terakhir almarhumah untuk ayahnya. Netta disambut curiga dan dianggap pembawa musibah karena kampungnya sedang dilanda teror Lampor, setan pencabut nyawa yang membawa keranda terbang.

programme.title: Dendam Sarakit S1 Ep8
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Tat dan bapanya menuju ke rumah Rafiq untuk mencari Zana. Mereka menjumpai Zana sedang bercakap seorang diri di depan rumah Rafiq. Rafiq pula mendapati bahawa Sarakit berkelakuan pelik seperti marah dengan Rafiq kerana membeli barang-barang untuk bayi dan membuat ukiran kayu untuk bayi. Sarakit meminta Rafiq berjanji untuk tidak mengalih kasih sayangnya kepada bayi yang bakal lahir tetapi hanya tertumpu pada dirinya sahaja. Pada satu malam, Tat mendapati Zana di luar rumah dengan patung kayu yang dikatakan dihadiahkan oleh wanita cantik berbaju putih. Tat tidak tahan keluarganya sering diganggu hantu tenggek dan mengesyaki Sarakit adalah puncanya. Dalam keadaan marah, Tat telah membawa parang menuju ke rumah Sarakit walaupun ditegah oleh Jali. Keesokan harinya, mayat Tat dijumpai terkulai di atas pokok.

programme.title: Hunter Killer
programme.desc: Kapal selam kelas Los Angeles AS USS Tampa Bay hilang ketika membayangi kapal selam kelas Akula Rusia Konek di Artik. Laksamana Muda John Fisk (Common) menghantar kapal selam kelas Virginia USS Arkansas, di bawah perintah Komander Joe Glass (Gerard Butler) yang baru dinaikkan pangkat dan tidak ortodoks untuk menyiasat. Pada masa yang sama, pasukan Navy SEAL di bawah pimpinan Leftenan Bill Beaman dihantar untuk memerhatikan pangkalan tentera laut Rusia secara diam-diam. Apabila mereka tiba di pangkalan tentera laut, mereka menyaksikan menteri pertahanan Dmitri Durov melakukan rampasan kuasa dan menawan Presiden Rusia Zakarin, dan dengan cepat menyedari bahawa Durov berhasrat untuk mencetuskan perang.

Pada suatu hari semasa memburu seorang penjenayah, tubuhnya secara tidak dapat dijelaskan telah dirasuk oleh jiwa seorang penipu yang licik Gong Soo Chang. Dua jiwa antagonis berakhir dalam perkongsian penyelesaian jenayah yang pelik. Keadaan menjadi lebih rumit apabila seorang wartawan impulsif, Song Ji An, menyertai siasatan.

programme.title: Ular
programme.desc: Sekumpulan pemenang cabutan bertuah memenangi percutian impian di resort pulau yang kelihatan indah, hanya untuk mendapati diri mereka terperangkap di pulau yang dipenuhi ular maut.

programme.title: Haq
programme.desc: "Haq" ialah sebuah filem aksi mengenai perjuangan antara kebaikan dan kejahatan. Haq (Zul Huzaimy) dan Bad (Adi Putra) dikurniakan kuasa istimewa. Bad, yang menjadi anak angkat oleh keluarga Haq, mempunyai kebencian yang mendalam terhadap Haq. Dia menggunakan kuasanya untuk mencemarkan nama baik Haq. Bagaimanapun, Haq enggan menggunakan kuasanya untuk menghalang Bad sehingga dia mendapati dirinya terperangkap oleh yang terakhir.

programme.title: Di Sebalik Wajah S1 Ep9

Dalam masa yang sama, Nadia berjaya menyakinkan Amir untuk bekerjasama dengan Red bagi membersihkan imej syarikatnya.

programme.title: Lampor: Keranda Terbang
programme.desc: Edwin dan Netta bersama dua anak mereka, Agam dan Sekar, kembali ke kampung Netta di Temanggung. Kampung yang telah ditinggal Netta 25 tahun bersama ibunya yang marah akan perbuatan sesat ayahnya. Netta harus menyampaikan pesan terakhir almarhumah untuk ayahnya. Netta disambut curiga dan dianggap pembawa musibah karena kampungnya sedang dilanda teror Lampor, setan pencabut nyawa yang membawa keranda terbang.

programme.title: Hunter Killer
programme.desc: Kapal selam kelas Los Angeles AS USS Tampa Bay hilang ketika membayangi kapal selam kelas Akula Rusia Konek di Artik. Laksamana Muda John Fisk (Common) menghantar kapal selam kelas Virginia USS Arkansas, di bawah perintah Komander Joe Glass (Gerard Butler) yang baru dinaikkan pangkat dan tidak ortodoks untuk menyiasat. Pada masa yang sama, pasukan Navy SEAL di bawah pimpinan Leftenan Bill Beaman dihantar untuk memerhatikan pangkalan tentera laut Rusia secara diam-diam. Apabila mereka tiba di pangkalan tentera laut, mereka menyaksikan menteri pertahanan Dmitri Durov melakukan rampasan kuasa dan menawan Presiden Rusia Zakarin, dan dengan cepat menyedari bahawa Durov berhasrat untuk mencetuskan perang.

programme.title: Seekers Underground Ep5
programme.desc: Seekers kembali dengan nama baru Seekers Underground. Dengan teknologi baru serta tinjaun ke lokasi yang belum pernah diterokai

programme.title: 4bia
programme.desc: Empat kisah seram berkisar tentang mangsa kemalangan, remaja yang dibuli, cerita hantu dan puteri yang telah meninggal dunia

programme.title: Jangan Ikut Aku Ep2
programme.desc: Akil yang dihinggap sakit gatal-gatal pulang ke kampung untuk mencari penawar. Akil berubat dengan bomoh Tok Misai dan juga diberi sebentuk cincin permata hijau. Malangnya keesokan hari, Tok Misai terbunuh semasa berkelahi dengan Pawang Anjang Itam yang sedang mencari cincin 4 keramat yang berada dalam milik Tok Misai. Sepulangnya ke bandar, Akil dapati gatal-gatalnya hilang dan diberitahu kepada kawannya Nabil. Nabil mengingatkan Akil supaya berjaga-jaga kerana kebiasaannya Tok Bomoh ada membela hantu. Akil mula percaya cakap Nabil kerana dia pernah diusik oleh lembaga pada waktu malam. Akil pulang sekali lagi ke kampung untuk menemui Tok Misai tetapi diberitahu Tok Misai telah mati terbunuh. Di masa sama Siti anak Tok Misai sedang mencari siapa yang terakhir berubat dengan ayahnya.

programme.title: Spides Ep1
programme.desc: Seorang wanita muda bernama NORA BERGER tersedar daripada koma tanpa ingatan tentang kehidupan lamanya, jelas telah menjadi mangsa dadah parti baharu BLIS. Ibu bapanya, HELEN dan RON, menggesa DR. HERTER untuk membebaskan anak perempuan mereka dari wad hospital Institut TORSEN yang berprestij. Setelah pulang, dan dengan bantuan adik lelakinya, FINN, Nora mendapat semula ingatannya, perlahan-lahan.

programme.title: Corpse Party
programme.desc: Pada suatu malam hujan selepas perayaan sekolah, sekumpulan pelajar dari Sekolah Menengah Kisaragi memutuskan untuk mempersembahkan pesona "Sachiko Ever After", yang akan menyatukan mereka selama-lamanya sebagai kawan. Setelah upacara itu selesai, gempa bumi mengejut membawa mereka ke Heavenly Host, sebuah sekolah rendah yang dirobohkan berikutan pembunuhan dan kehilangan beberapa kakitangan dan pelajarnya.

programme.title: Lie After Lie Ep20
programme.desc: Woo Joo diperiksa di hospital dan ternyata dia menghidap penyakit serius. Dia hanya boleh bertahan jika dia mendapat pemindahan paru-paru tetapi Ji Min bukan jodoh. Eun Su diuji untuk melihat sama ada miliknya sepadan dengan Woo Joo.

programme.title: Spides Ep2
programme.desc: Detektif David Leonhart dan Nique Navar melawat Nora. Dia tidak dapat menjawab soalan mereka tentang Blis dan Rapture kerana kehilangan ingatannya. Nora kelihatan gugup, membuatkan dirinya curiga. Polis bertanya kepada ibu bapanya mengapa dia dibawa ke Institut Torsen, di semua tempat.

programme.title: The Rescue
programme.desc: Kecemasan berlaku pada pelantar penggerudian luar pesisir yang akan menyebabkannya terbalik dan tenggelam. Unit Tindak Balas Kecemasan berlumba mengikut masa dalam misi menyelamat helikopter di tengah-tengah letupan dan kebakaran berbahaya. Kapten Gao Qian mesti bekerjasama dengan lancar dengan juruterbang helikopternya Zhao Cheng untuk menyelamatkan mangsa yang terselamat menggunakan taktik yang paling hebat dan berbahaya.

programme.title: Suara Kekasih
programme.desc: Percintaan yang ditentang keluarga kerana perbezaan darjat membuatkan Ayu dan Taufiq terpaksa membawa haluan berbeza. Ayu, penyanyi di kelab malam jatuh cinta dengan Taufiq, pengurus syarikat insuran yang berasal dari keluarga kaya. Ditentang oleh ibu Taufiq, mereka merasakan restu keluarga amat penting dan terpaksa membuat keputusan penting untuk masa depan mereka.

programme.title: Rentak Desa
programme.desc: Pencemaran alam menyebabkan penduduk kampung mula menunjuk perasaan. Mat Desa dan Wairah seringkali berasa bahawa penduduk di situ hanya hidup atas empati pemaju. Hanya kerana ingin membuat jalan raya, bukit dan pokok ditebang manakala sungai dicemari sisa bahan toksik - menyebabkan ikan mati dan beracun. Sebuah penemuan merungkai segalanya.

programme.title: Ceritaku Ceritamu
programme.desc: Gadis kampung yang memasang cita-cita tinggi untuk mencari pekerjaan di ibu kota. Berpengetahuan dalam bidang fesyen, dia ingin membina masa depan yang lebih cerah buatnya. Setelah berhijrah, Hasnah/Ana bertemu seorang lelaki dan menjalin hubungan bersamanya - namun dia sudah berkahwin dan mempunyai anak sebaya dengannya.

programme.title: Bayangan Cinta
programme.desc: Pertemuan dua bekas kekasih, Auzy dan Akhbar selepas 18 tahun membangkitkan perasaan lama. Walau perasaan cinta masih kuat, hubungan mereka tidak dapat diteruskan kerana Akhbar sudah pun berkahwin. Suratan takdir mengatakan sebaliknya apabila Auzy kini mengajar anak kepada Akhbar, Andy.

programme.title: Ali Setan
programme.desc: Ali pelajar universiti yang nakal dan suka bergurau berjumpa Asmidar ketika dalam perjalanan ke universiti. Ali selalu mencari jalan untuk mengusik Asmidar, lama kelamaan perasaan cinta mula berputik antara mereka berdua. Konflik mula terjadi apabila Ali sebenarnya sudah berkahwin dengan Tipah namun atas sebab terpaksa.

programme.title: Suara Kekasih
programme.desc: Percintaan yang ditentang keluarga kerana perbezaan darjat membuatkan Ayu dan Taufiq terpaksa membawa haluan berbeza. Ayu, penyanyi di kelab malam jatuh cinta dengan Taufiq, pengurus syarikat insuran yang berasal dari keluarga kaya. Ditentang oleh ibu Taufiq, mereka merasakan restu keluarga amat penting dan terpaksa membuat keputusan penting untuk masa depan mereka.

programme.title: Permintaan Terakhir
programme.desc: Salina terpaksa menjalani kehidupan baharu setelah ibunya berkahwin dengan bapa kepada Rohani yang merupakan musuh Salina di sekolah. Salina terpaksa mencari jalan untuk mendapat perhatian keluarganya. Keadaan ini berlanjutan sehingga dia mendapat tahu dirinya menghidap penyakit barah otak. Salina merahsiakan perkara ini daripada keluarganya, namun ia terbongkar setelah Rohani terdengar doa yang dibaca Salina.

programme.title: Dewi Cinta
programme.desc: Patah hati kerana teman lelakinya curang, Dewi cuba untuk membunuh diri. Sebelum terlambat, Dewi segera menyedari bahawa usahanya itu hanyalah sia-sia. Dia bertemu dengan Arman lalu mereka berdua jatuh cinta dan menjalinkan hubungan. Bekas teman lelaki Dewi, Micky muncul kembali menagih cinta darinya kerana masih tidak boleh melupakan Dewi. Pilihan terpaksa dibuat antara Arman atau Micky.

programme.title: Bayi Tabung
programme.desc: Setelah mengharungi satu peristiwa yang menghimpit kehidupan, Jelina ditawarkan untuk menyewakan rahimnya dengan bayaran tinggi oleh sepasang suami isteri dari Malaysia yang tidak punya anak secara biasa. Tawaran harga yang tinggi membuatkan Jelina bersetuju untuk menerima titipan embrio itu sehingga lahir. Setelah bayi itu lahir timbul pula satu masalah kerana Jelina merasa bahawa bayi itu adalah darah dagingnya.

programme.title: Tuan Besar
programme.desc: Tuan Wahid sering menggunakan darjat untuk bersikap kasar dengan pekerjanya dan mengambil kesempatan terhadap Rokiah. Rokiah, seorang janda mempunyai anak bernama Jamilah. Jamil, anak Tuan Wahid pula jatuh cinta dengan Jamilah. Ini menimbulkan konflik antara mereka berdua lalu datang Tuan Besar untuk menyelesaikan konflik itu.

programme.title: Bintang Malam
programme.desc: Selepas dua belas tahun berlayar, Yazid dan Johari akhirnya pulang semula ke tanah air. Yazid pulang ke kampung manakala Johari pergi ke Kuala Lumpur dan bertemu Haslinda, Shima dan Aida. Bersimpati dengan nasib Haslinda, Johari ingin membantunya. Yazid pula keluar mencari Aisah di bandar - tetapi berdepan dengan pelbagai konflik dan tragedi.

programme.title: Memori
programme.desc: Seorang Dato yang berpengaruh bersama dua orang anaknya yang mempunyai masalah tersendiri. Anak perempuannya bergelut dengan dunia dadah manakala anak lelakinya terlampau menyukai dunia permotoran sehingga obses akan perkara itu. Kehilangan bapa mereka akhirnya menimbulkan rasa sesal dalam diri mereka.

programme.title: Simfoni Duniaku
programme.desc: Iskandar, pemuda yang suka berfoya-foya akhirnya merasai kebahagiaan alam percintaan. Perkenalannya bersama Zuraida telah membuatkan dia jatuh cinta. Namun, terpaksa berdepan rintangan apabila Iskandar telah dijodohkan bersama anak perempuan kepada rakan niaga bapanya. Liku-liku percintaan dan tentangan terpaksa dihadapi oleh dua pasangan bercinta.

programme.title: Commitment
programme.desc: When a North Korean spy infiltrates South Korea as a teenage defector, the South Korean government begin tracking him while his own government sends a vicious assassin to eliminate him.

programme.title: Innocent Witness
programme.desc: A housekeeper is charged with murder. Her attorney is surprised to learn the only witness to the crime is a teenage girl with Asperger's. Will the girl be able to provide a valid statement?

programme.title: A Man Who Was Superman
programme.desc: Soo-jung met a man who claimed himself as a "superman" and loves to give a helping hand to people in need. She then realizes the story behind his seemingly weird behavior...

programme.title: Innocence
programme.desc: A hotshot lawyer uncovers the conspiracy of a small village while defending her estranged mother, who has Alzheimer's disease and accused of killing the attendees at her husband’s funeral.

programme.title: The Goblin
programme.desc: After ten years in jail, Doohyun is released and wants nothing more than to live an ordinary life, but when his old partner kidnaps his daughter, the long-hidden Goblin inside him awakes.

programme.title: The Odd Family: Zombie On Sale
programme.desc: When a pharmaceutical company's illegal experiments inadvertently create a zombie, the quirky Park family discovers an interesting side effect to the virus and tries to profit from it.

programme.title: Exit
programme.desc: A rock climber tries to save the day after a mad scientist releases a toxic gas that leaves thousands stranded in skyscrapers in Seoul district.

programme.title: 71: Into The Fire
programme.desc: 71 student-soldiers fight an impossible war against the elite 766 Commando Brigade and turn the tide of the Korean War.

programme.title: The Accidental Detective
programme.desc: A crime-enthusiast blogger and a veteran detective team up to prove the innocence of their mutual friend who's been framed for a horrific murder.

programme.title: Countdown
programme.desc: A debt collector has liver cancer and has to get a liver transplant in 10 days. A seductive swindler agrees to donate her liver only if he tracks down the man who put her in prison.

programme.title: Mr. Housewife
programme.desc: A dad enjoys his daily chores and taking care of his daughter at home. But when he faces financial trouble, he joins a TV game show to win the jackpot while pretending to be a housewife.

programme.title: Heung-Boo: The Revolutionist
programme.desc: Set in the Joseon dynasty, a satirical street play becomes popular among the people. Heung-boo, its author, gains fame and is sought by conflicting powers who want to use him for their own agendas.

programme.title: The Witch: Part 2. The Other One

programme.title: Taste of Life (T) Ep909910
programme.desc: Chu-Tsai,Chao and his wife Chin-hsiu,Li have five children. Devoted all his life into developing soy sauce products, Chu-Tsai very much hopes that one of his kids can follow his footsteps and take over his business, but he also respects their own passions and aspirations. Because of their father’s invention dream, the Chao brothers’ lives are about to change… Chin-Pang,Chou used to be Chin-Hsiu’s lover, and has been Chu-Tsai’s long-time business rival. Seeing Chu-Tsai not only successfully keep the patents of soy sauce products, but also has all the support and assistance from his children, Chin-Pang, filled with bitterness, has been crushing and attacking Chu-Tsai in every way. Hsin-Ta, Chu-Tsai’s eldest son, couldn’t bear to see his father suffer, so he quit his job to take over the family business. To everyone’s surprise, Chu-Tsai discovers that Hsin-Ta is actually Chin-Pang’s son! Finding out that the enemy is actually his biological father devastated Hsin-Ta, and this also drives a wedge between Chin-pang and his son Hsiao-Ming, as he feels threatened. Chu-tsai’s second son Ying-kai has always set his goal to reach the top of his career. Vacillating between Mei-mei and Ying-hui, Ying-kai also finds himself caught in between the feud of two families; however, this opens new business opportunities for him. On the other hand, Hsin-ta fulfills Chu-tsai’s dream; but he is more confused than ever about family love and romance love… All he knows is that with the family’s support, his determination and conviction, he can build a future of his own!

programme.title: Back To Home (M) Ep30
programme.desc: When the news reached her that the old village leader had passed away, Xiao Li, who was a personal shopper, stuffed a few things into her Hermes bag and, clutching the lucky salt he had once given her, set out for her home town wearing her Prada high-heeled shoes. That night A-Jian, who was helping out in a Japanese restaurant, also jumped on the bus and headed home as soon as he received the news. In his will, the old man divided up his salt fields among the villagers, but on the condition that A-Jian and Xiao Li get married. When they heard this, A-Jian and Xiao Li found themselves immediately surrounded…

With that single dream in mind, An An never even thought of becoming anything more than the ordinary girl she had always been. But all that changed the day You Yuan Le walked into her life.

programme.title: Taichung Player (M) Ep78
programme.desc: Chin-Lan Chang & Top Social Media Infulencer travel & explore Taichong!

programme.title: CNY-Have A Nice Dream (M) Ep98
programme.desc: Let’s go for a most chillax trip during Chinese New Year. Hosts have planned a trip to enjoy the greatest getaway that nature is gifted and share the most beautiful trail in Taiwan. They even will share some tips on how to cook CNY dishes at the camping area.

programme.title: CNY-Super Ethnic Chinese(M) Ep1
programme.desc: The hosts will be divided into two teams. Each team will lead the artists from 2 stations for a 4-hour talent’s PK battle on stage. Let’s enjoy and feel the aura of powerful vocals & performances!

programme.title: Mr.Player (M) Ep432
programme.desc: Depending on the locations of the missions, Jacky Wu, the leader of the home team, invites various celebrities to take on challenges and bring you excitement every week.

programme.title: Piggy's Counter-Attack (M) Ep70
programme.desc: A rich father, who built his fortune from nothing, goes bankrupt overnight when his investments fail. His children are knocked out of heaven and have to launch a counterattack.

programme.title: Heroic Duo
programme.desc: Police officer Ken needs help to solve a grisly crime that the offender has no recollection of committing. Ken seeks out Jack, a former psychologist who is now imprisoned. Forming an uneasy truce, this unconventional duo sets out to find the man responsible. It is at this time that Ken falls into a trap set up by Jack…

programme.title: Napping Kid
programme.desc: Xiao Ru’s financial analysis for a bank client was stolen online. A ransom has to be paid within three days or else the document would be disclosed. To protect the client’s data, the company brings in the police to investigate. In the meantime, an analyst disappears and the Technical Director resigns. Is there a bigger crisis lurking behind?

programme.title: Golden Job
programme.desc: A group of former mercenaries reunite to plan an epic heist: boosting a truckload of medicine held by a foreign intelligence agency to supply a refugee camp in need. When they find the truck is filled with stolen gold however, they realize they have been double-crossed by one of their own and putting the situation right will be an all-out war.

programme.title: I Still Remember
programme.desc: Chi is a property agent who leads an aimless and unfulfilling life until he reunites with his P.E. teacher, Wong, from primary school. Despite his illness, Wong insists on keeping his promise of completing a 10K marathon to his late wife. Inspired by Wong, Chi brings himself to his feet and finds the courage to cheer himself on!

programme.title: The Trough
programme.desc: Yu Chau is a cop who has gone very deeply undercover within the triads. When he accidentally kills one of his pals in an operation, he runs off into the wild to lick his wounds. Upon his return, he teams up with fellow officers Jim and Jackie to catch a triad Boss, only to unveil collusion with government officials at the highest level.

programme.title: Wine War
programme.desc: A Chinese wine expert residing in France is contacted by his childhood buddy in China to help him bid for a famous bottle of vintage wine in an auction. Little did he realize he is about to enter an age-old feud between rivaling vineyards and discover a historical mystery that might shatter the whole wine industry.

programme.title: Peace Breaker
programme.desc: Police officer Gao accidentally kills a pedestrian on the way to his mother's funeral. He tries to dispose the body by hiding it in his mother's coffin. As the pedestrian turns out to be a wanted person and a police officer witnessed the accident, Gao is forced to bring his body back to the police station. Can the case be settled so easily?

programme.title: Aberdeen
programme.desc: The Cheng family embodies a microcosm of Hong Kong, with its contradictions between tradition and modernity, superstition and materialism, family and individual. The movie reveals troubled characters dealing with their own issues in the city, from the eldest, Taoist priest patriarch Dong; to the youngest, the bullied elementary schooler Chloe.

programme.title: 12 Golden Ducks
programme.desc: This is a comeback story about the misadventures of a group of gigolos, led by Future, trying to make their mark in Hong Kong. As with any profession, they have their share of setbacks, but their ability to find laughter within the tears reflects the drive, passion and the indomitable spirit of the Hong Kong people.

programme.title: Incredible Monk, Dragon Return, The
programme.desc: Ko Yan Kit is a famous General in Song dynasty. Due to public pressure, Ko dare not confess his feeling for his first love Fung Yee, who is forced to work in a brothel. Feeling helpless, he asks a monk for help. Everything goes smoothly, but when Fung Yee is suddenly killed, the monk must travel to the underworld to save Ko’s first love!

programme.title: Detective Chinatown 2
programme.desc: Qin Feng was tricked by Tang Ran to participate in the "World Detective Contest" in New York's Chinatown. Their task is to find the murderer of the grandson of Godfather, Uncle Qi. When famous detectives from all over the world investigate the case, two other cases occurred with a very similar modus operandi…

programme.title: Septet: The Story of Hong Kong
programme.desc: Seven of Hong Kong's most revered directors, all with distinctly unique styles, come together for the first time to compose a symphony of stories for their city from the 50s to the future.

programme.title: Girls VS Gangsters
programme.desc: A bachelorette weekend spins hilariously out of control when three friends wake up naked on a beach and find themselves handcuffed to a mysterious briefcase, with local gangsters in pursuit. They must regain memories of what happened that weekend if they hope to go back home safely!

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon
programme.desc: Infamous real-life drug kingpin Crippled Ho came to Hong Kong as an illegal immigrant in 1963, and ruthlessly carved an empire from the chaotic underworld of drug dealers and corrupt police who ruled the city under notorious detective Lee Rock.

programme.title: Flirting Scholar 2
programme.desc: The movie tells the story of Tang Bo Hu and his three buddies before they become the four great talents in Jiangnan. Tang Bo Hu encounters a beautiful girl when studying in a monastery and they quickly fall in love, but her hidden identity is accidentally unveiled when Tang and friends uncover a conspiracy at the monastery.

programme.title: Just 1 Day
programme.desc: Mosaic, an urban sketcher, is suffering from ALS and wants to create some fond memories as his condition worsens. When Mosaic reunites with his old classmate Angelfish, whom he has a crush on since primary school, he asks her to fulfill his one last wish by becoming his girlfriend for just one day. Will Angelfish say “yes”?

programme.title: Hand Rolled Cigarette
programme.desc: A retired British-Chinese soldier becomes a target in a triad manhunt when he takes in a young South Asian man who carries a bag of stolen drugs. Forced to live together, the two men transcend conflicts and cultural differences to form a beautiful friendship in this poignant tale of loyalty and brotherhood.

programme.title: Reunion Dinner
programme.desc: Chao Yang and Zi Hong are soon to wed but both have not met the other’s parents. When a client requests for a livestream of their reunion dinner to promote his products, it set the stage for their parents’ first meeting. Estranged from his mother, Yang decides to rent a family for the dinner which results in a series of mishaps and hilarity.

programme.title: Mama's Affair
programme.desc: Former talent manager Mei Fung stays home to take care of her husband and son after retirement. She decides to re-enter the entertainment business to find her value in life, and successfully transforms a local restaurant delivery boy, Fong Ching, into a young pop idol. This makes her teenage son, Jonathan, intensely jealous of Fong Ching.

programme.title: Endgame
programme.desc: A killer and a stage actor accidentally swapped their identities at a bathhouse. The actor must complete the killer’s mission while the killer thinks he is a hopeless actor after losing his memory during the accident. When the killer strives to become a successful stage actor, he also starts to recall what has happened…

programme.title: All's Well End's Well 2011
programme.desc: Popular make-up artist Sammy is hired as the CEO of a cosmetics company with all women staff. As he is clueless with women, he invites Arnold, a fellow make-up artist, to join and help him. Though Arnold might appear to be a woman's magnet, his heart still lingers with his first love, Mona.

programme.title: Fierce Cop
programme.desc: To save his son who has been kidnapped by human traffickers, police officer Zhang relentlessly hunts them down and accidentally finds himself implicated in a major child abduction case. In the process, he teams up with a mysterious lady to crack the international crime syndicate and rescue his son.

programme.title: The Monkey is Back
programme.desc: The savior of the people, Stone Monkey, has given hope to a desperate little girl which he promises to realize. Years later, Stone Monkey is defeated in a battle with the three-eyed God of War, causing him to lose his power and falls into the mortal world. Can he fulfill his promise to the girl and stop the God of Wood from destroying earth?

programme.title: Kung Fu Monster
programme.desc: In the Ming Dynasty, the Bruneian Empire offers a monster as a gift to the nation. Imperial guard Ocean is tasked to train it, but realizing it is a kind creature by nature, he releases it secretly so that it will not become a killing beast. His action prompts a frenzy hunt for the monster when the palace puts a hefty bounty for its return…

programme.title: Kill Mobile
programme.desc: Seven friends get together and decide to play a game where they must share all the messages, calls and app notifications on each other's cell phones. Hilarity and drama follows as everyone's secrets are unveiled throughout the evening, and the seven friends find themselves more like strangers to each other than ever before!

programme.title: New Kung Fu Cult Master 1
programme.desc: Wu Dang Sect’s Zhang Chui Shan’s son, Zhang Wu Ji, finds himself accidentally embroiled in the fight for the Dragon Sabre. When he unwittingly learns the powerful martial arts skills from the Jiuyin scriptures, Wu Ji proceeds to help the Six Major sects fight against the corrupt government.

programme.title: Infernal Affairs
programme.desc: Yan is a police mole in the triad and joined them before he graduated from the police academy, while Ming is a triad mole in the police since young. Leading parallel lives, both men feel increasingly trapped in their false surroundings, and a series of cat-and-mouse chases ensue as both the triad and the police compete to uncover the other’s mole.

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon II: Wild Wild Bunch
programme.desc: Starring four Hong Kong Film Awards Best Actors, Simon Yam, Louis Koo, Tony Leung Ka Fai and Gordon Lam, this action-thriller follows the real-life kidnapping events that terrorized Hong Kong’s elite in the 1990s by serial billionaire-kidnapper Logan and his gang.

programme.title: Detective Vs. Sleuths
programme.desc: Hong Kong is rocked by a series of cold-blooded murders whose victims are runaway suspects of unsolved cases. The group of killers calls themselves “The Chosen Sleuths". Former top detective Lee vows to bring the brutal killers to justice and prove himself to be the real “Chosen Sleuth” instead of a lunatic.

programme.title: Think Big Big
programme.desc: Moon is a plus-sized girl working happily as a mascot at a theme park. That is until one day she accidentally joins a weight loss competition, with her remarkable transformation turning her into the "Nation’s Goddess". Netizens have their eyes glued on her, turning her life upside down, and Moon has to find a way to be happy again.

programme.title: Enter the Fat Dragon
programme.desc: Donnie Yen plays a Hong Kong police officer who is highly skilled in martial arts but balloons to more than 200 pounds after his fiancé left him. His boss can only assign simple tasks to him like escorting a criminal to Japan, but can he complete it?

programme.title: Table for Six
programme.desc: In this comedy, three brothers reside in a home inherited from their late parents. The eldest brother insists they have dinner at home every night as a family, but tensions begin to rise when their girlfriends join in as well. Love, friendship, jealousy and complicated relationships are all on the menu for this table for six!

programme.title: Tropicana Interlude
programme.desc: Ping and Su are lovers who operate a travel agency specializing in Southeast Asian holidays. Tung, a school mistress, and her students join a guided tour lead by Ping. During the trip, a spoiled kid Li is attracted to Ping but Su thinks Ping has fallen for Tung and leaves. How will Ping deal with the situation and ends up happily back with Su?

programme.title: The Supreme Swordsman
programme.desc: After beating several famous swordsmen, Chin Wu-hsin (Pai Piao) of the Mo Shan clan challenges Supreme Swordsman (Wang Jung) to a duel, hoping to win his title, and is beaten and humiliated. The winner taunts him to find a Supreme Sword made by Old Eagle, a famous sword-maker (Ku Feng). When his offer to buy a sword from Old Eagle, is turned down, he challenges Old Eagle to a duel, and snatches his sword in a foul play. Old Eagle's own son Shih Yen-peh (Derek Yee) vows to avenge for his father...

programme.title: The Merry Wife
programme.desc: A 17-year old schoolgirl marries her 35-year-old teacher. Comedy ensues when they attempt to keep their relationship a secret despite being in the same school. When they discover unwanted suitors going after their other halves, jealousy threatens to expose their marriage any minute!

programme.title: The Knight Of Knights
programme.desc: Wen Su Chen, the leader of seven knights, sends his six sworn brothers to investigate a monastery. Unfortunately, they are killed by an abbot who plans to murder Inspector Lin. Wen saved Lin and battles the abbot to avenge his dead sworn brothers. With Lin and his army’s help, they bring down the ruthless monks in the monastery.

programme.title: The Amorous Lotus Pan
programme.desc: Adapted from the renowned Chinese novel, The Water Margin, this is the story of a poor and beautiful girl Lotus Pan, who is raped by her master and had to be married off to a midget who treats her badly. Lost and lonely, Pan unwittingly becomes a pawn in the game of lust between her husband’s playboy brother Wu Song, and a murderous man Men Ching.

programme.title: My Young Auntie
programme.desc: An elderly landowner marries the young Dai Nan to keep his inheritance away from his unscrupulous nephew before he dies. When Dai Nan brings along the deed to meet his other nephew, a series of amusing incidents happen with this “young” auntie, the nephew and his son. Kara won Best Actress in the first Hong Kong Film Awards for her role as Dai Nan.

programme.title: West Chamber
programme.desc: The story is based on a famous Chinese opera. A young impoverished scholar, Zhang, is enchanted by Hong, the daughter of an influential family whom he meets in a temple. The young couple faces the threat of separation due to her family’s objection, so Hong’s maid secretly helps to arrange their rendezvous in the West Chamber!

programme.title: Golden Swallow
programme.desc: A heroine finds herself in a love triangle with a swordsman and a warrior. They team up to conquer the evil forces of the martial arts world. However, she is caught between both men whom she admires when facing a deadly duel.

programme.title: Diau Charn
programme.desc: In the Han Dynasty, the tyrannical Prime Minister Dong Zuo takes control of the country, so Minister Wang plots to take him down using Diau Charn’s beauty. Wang arranges for her to be Dong’s concubine as he knows Dong’s adopted son Lu Bu is in love with her, turning them against each other. Lu Bu ends up killing Dong Zuo to be with Diau Charn.

programme.title: Brothers From The Walled City
programme.desc: Two orphaned brothers growing up in Kowloon's Walled City - the place where people are forced to live with indecent businesses of sex, gambling and drugs controlled by triads - take very different life paths. Chin works at a cabaret but keeps away from sins, while Kang is drawn to the sleazy underworld. Are their destinies shaped by the “walls”?

programme.title: Raw Courage
programme.desc: After the Ming Emperor is overthrown and his infant son was put in the care of the Black Dragon Society, a traitorous martial arts clan attacks the society, forcing an inexperienced pair of swordsman and swordswoman to flee with the infant. Their journey to deliver the infant to safety is filled with dangers that would require help from other allies…

programme.title: Empress Wu
programme.desc: Wu Ze Tian is a beautiful and talented concubine of Emperor Tang at age 14. She becomes a nun after he died but has two sons with the new Emperor Tang Gao Zong. The Empress asks Wu to team up with her against Consort Xiao, but is set up and dethroned by Wu, who also kills her two sons. After the Emperor’s death, Wu becomes the first woman Emperor.

programme.title: Trilogy Of Swordsmanship
programme.desc: A kung fu anthology film consisting of three stories: a man embarrasses himself while trying to prove his worth to the father of the woman he loves; a courtesan in love with a general will need to deliver a notorious bandit in exchange for him not being executed; and a group of bandits forms a plan to rescue a new friend from being executed.

programme.title: Return Of The Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: This sequel makes for more bittersweet laughs and heart-wrenching misfortune, as Ah Niu gets out of the jail to find his true love becoming the wife of an abusive husband, and his uncle further exploits his naive nature.

programme.title: The Treasure Hunters
programme.desc: Fans of the international star Alexander Fu Sheng were aghast. Their idol had broken both his legs and was recuperating. Everyone wondered: would he be able to return to the action comedies for which he was so famous? This movie was the answer, and it left no doubt that he had made a full recovery. Liu Chia-yung, brother of preeminent martial arts moviemaker Liu Chia-liang, was famous in his own right for kung-fu comedies, and he out-did himself with this one. Imagine Bob Hope and Bing Crosby with the skills of Jet Li and Jackie Chan, and you’ve got an idea of the fun and fury inherent in this delightful tale of two con men vying for a horde of hidden gold. Add to the mix a Shaolin monk (played by "Master Killer" Gordon Liu Chia-hui), a powerfully brutal villain (Wang Lung-wei), and his equally dangerous mute sister (future director Yang Tsing-tsing), and you’ve got one of the most internationally loved kung-fu capers ever made.

programme.title: The Human Goddess
programme.desc: This is a love story between an alluring fairy, Seventh Sister, who comes down from heaven to experience life in 70’s Hong Kong, and a man who is running a debt laden orphanage. A heartless tycoon plans to take over the orphanage for its land but has to deal with Seventh Sister’s magical powers as she aims to protect it from falling into his hands!

programme.title: The Silent Swordsman
programme.desc: This is adapted from Louis Cha’s “The Book and the Sword”. A young swordsman is tasked to lead a patriotic secret society to fight the traitorous general who colludes with the enemy. At the same time, he encounters a female warrior and two beautiful princesses, and is caught between all their affections for him.

programme.title: The Happy Trio
programme.desc: Li Ching plays, Ah Chiao, a girl from a rural village stranded in the city, who befriends a kind-hearted tramp and a retired actor. They are all poor, but Ah Chiao’s fortune change for the better when she becomes a singer. However, she ultimately learns money can't buy happiness.

programme.title: Opium And The Kung-Fu Master
programme.desc: Tie Qiao San, head of the Ten Guangdong Tigers, is an honourable master with many disciples. As opium becomes popular among the nobles, Tie starts taking it and gradually harms his body. When an opium house’s owner defeats Tie in a fight and he is only saved from being killed by his disciple, Tie vows to quit opium and get back on his feet.

programme.title: The Dream Of The Red Chamber
programme.desc: Adapted from the great Chinese classic novel of the same name, the son of renowned Jia family, Bao Yu, is deeply in love with his cousin, Dai Yu. However, his mother disapproves of their relationship and plots to arrange Bao Yu to marry another rich girl, resulting in a tragic ending for the perfect couple.

programme.title: The Warlord
programme.desc: A bandit became a warlord in northern China by helping Russia fight against Japan. Due to his ignorance and silly behaviour, he is seen as a joke to everyone. The warlord is finally killed by the daughter of a troupe master whom he had killed for no reason, bringing a befitting end to a traitor.

programme.title: Heads For Sale
programme.desc: Hua is an upright and brave swordswoman who will stand up against villains and do anything for Luo, the man she loves. When Luo is sent to jail by the corrupted police, she sets out to free him and did not hesitate to chop off two bodyguards’ heads. In the process, she also stumbles across an old enemy of her father who is back seeking revenge.

programme.title: Fangs Of The Cobra
programme.desc: Incredibly, the title serpent is not a harbinger of horror, but actually the film's hero. This virtuous viper sniffs out bombs, fights gangs, battles a baby-killing rodent and even takes on a duplicitous woman. This one-of-a-kind thriller will be applauded by reptile fans everywhere.

programme.title: The Sword Stained With Royal Blood
programme.desc: Adapted from the novel by Jin Yong, havoc breaks out when a warrior on the run uncovers a sword, training manual, treasure map & a secret message on the body of a deceased martial arts master.

programme.title: Shadow Girl
programme.desc: A young swordswoman becomes invisible during the day and a monster at night after taking her grandma’s pill. She ruined the wedding of a bandit chief’s daughter using her powers and is hunted down by them for revenge. Will she escape the hunt?

programme.title: Mr. Funnybone Strikes Again
programme.desc: In this hilarious sequel, Mr Big Potato opens an old-fashioned Chinese clinic, but his traditional methods are rejected by the sceptics of modern Hong Kong. Enter his buddy Mr Funny bone to rescue his business!

programme.title: Clans Of Intrigue
programme.desc: One day, when the heroic outlaw Chu Liu Xiang is dining with his friend Monk Wu Hua, Gong from the Holy Water Palace accuses Chu of stealing the holy water and using it for various murders. Chu denies, and is given a month to find the murderer or be killed by Gong. To prove him innocence, Chu decides to investigate the case…

programme.title: The Magnificent Concubine
programme.desc: Yang Gui Fei is the beloved concubine of Emperor Tang Ming Huang, who is so besotted with her that he leaves the running of the country to Prime Minister Yang Guo Zhong, the brother of Yang Gui Fei. The Prime Minister is corrupt and cruel to the army, causing them to revolt and endanger the throne. Yang Gui Fei is also implicated and kills herself.

programme.title: Rendezvous With Death
programme.desc: Sun Chung had been recognized as an expert comedy and crime thriller director, but he was to gain even greater acclaim for his soulful, powerful, intelligent, and beautifully-made martial arts epics. This stands alongside The Deadly Breaking Sword and The Kung-fu Instructor as one of his very best. It's not so much the plot - a master swordsman protects a treasure chest on a dangerous journey - that makes this great, but what Sun does with it, inspiring the cast and crew to some of their finest work.

programme.title: Dawn Will Come
programme.desc: Liang Cai drugged the beautiful Qiu Rong and raped her, but promised to marry her after getting his parent’s consent. Since then, there is no news of his proposal and Qiu Rong confronts Liang Cai when she finds herself pregnant. This is when she discovers that he has already married a rich noble girl and even plans to kill her…

programme.title: Ambitious Kung Fu Girl
programme.desc: The lovely Michelle Mei Suet plays a spoiled girl Szu-szu who ignores her true love Yang Fan (Yuan Te) to go off in search of a swordsman Chin Ko (Chen Kuan-tai) she idolizes. The search sets off one great action scene after another, until she's threatened to be sold into slavery but Yang Fan arrives in the nick of time! This amusing and entertaining variation on the standard kung-fu film is definitely a winner.

programme.title: The Pearl Phoenix
programme.desc: In Huangmei Opera tradition, this movie tells the love story of Wen, who sells himself as a slave to a rich family, and Huo, the family’s young daughter. The lovers are kept apart by Huo’s stepmother and Huo escapes by dressing up as a man. Wen is framed and put into jail so Huo has to go back and rescue her lover!

programme.title: Shaolin Martial Arts
programme.desc: The Qing government assigns fighters to destroy Shaolin Temple and kill all the disciples, but two of them successfully escaped. They train under different masters and learn the Wing Chun and Hung Quan styles respectively, finally killing the fighters and taking revenge for the death of their fellow disciples.

programme.title: Twinkle Twinkle Little Star
programme.desc: A beautiful but ignorant woman is abducted by aliens but nobody believes her close encounter. While planning a suicide to prove herself, she meets a failed detective who is also planning his suicide. They change their minds about dying after finding each other and start to encounter bizarre adventures, before falling in love with each other.

programme.title: Maniyar Kudumbam
programme.desc: Kutti Maniyar, who belongs to a wealthy family, avoids working and lives off his inherited money and property. However, he decides to turn over a new leaf when he falls in love.

programme.title: Kamali From Nadukaveri
programme.desc: Kamali From Nadukkaveri embraces the Power and the Importance of Education for Women. Born as a Girl Child in a village called Nadukkaveri, How Kamali becomes the identity of the same village is what this film is all about.

programme.title: Sivalinga
programme.desc: Raheem gets killed when he tries to save a blind man in a train. When the police close the case stating suicide, Raheem's girlfriend asks Shivalingeshwaran, a CID officer, to investigate the death.

programme.title: Jai Hind 2
programme.desc: One man's fight to give good education to the poor.

programme.title: Aghavan
programme.desc: A police officer works undercover in Brihadeeswarar Temple in Thanjavur to protect its treasure from criminals who plan to loot the temple.

programme.title: Dhiya
programme.desc: When Thulasi gets pregnant before marriage, she is forced to abort the baby. Years later, her unborn baby's spirit kills all those who forced her mother to undergo an abortion.

programme.title: Irandam Ulagaporin Kadaisi Gundu
programme.desc: A lorry driver ends up in possession of an unexploded bomb that is being sought after by both the cops and pro-peace activists.

programme.title: Aghavan
programme.desc: A police officer works undercover in Brihadeeswarar Temple in Thanjavur to protect its treasure from criminals who plan to loot the temple.

programme.title: Devi 2
programme.desc: Devi starts suspecting her husband, Krishna, of infidelity when she notices him with two other women. However, she unearths a horrifying truth when she decides to investigate.

programme.title: Nota
programme.desc: A bachelor who is unaware of the political world is appointed a Chief Minister when his corrupt father retires.

programme.title: Karnan
programme.desc: Karnan, a fearless village youth, must fight for the rights of the conservative people of his village, due to the torture given by a police officer.

programme.title: Ainthu Ainthu Ainthu
programme.desc: Aravind unexpectedly loses his beloved girlfriend in a car accident. The strangest thing happens after the accident when people around him tell him no such person ever existed.

programme.title: Yaman
programme.desc: After losing his father to a bunch of scheming politicians, a young man decides to wade into the corrupt and unscrupulous world of politics to avenge his death.

programme.title: 8 Thotakkal
programme.desc: Sathya, an honest policeman, accidentally loses his service pistol while tailing a criminal. However, the thief who stole the pistol sells it to Murthy and he goes on a killing spree.

programme.title: Biscoth
programme.desc: After the death of his father, Raja begins to work in his father's company. He, however, finds his life changed when he befriends Janaki who narrates stories that come true for him.

programme.title: Akash Ganga
programme.desc: When a woman accepts the challenge of exposing an ashram, which claims to help its followers communicate with the dead, she gets haunted by an evil spirit that once tormented her family.

programme.title: Sowkarpet
programme.desc: The story is about two lovers who are murdered by villains. They come back as ghosts and start taking revenge on the people who killed them.

programme.title: Gorilla
programme.desc: Jeeva, Sathish, Venkat and Sadhik join hands in order to rob a bank with a chimpanzee as their accomplice. However, things do not go the way they planned.

programme.title: Veerame Vaagai Soodum
programme.desc: A normal man from a middle-class family questioning the authorities for abusing their powers.

programme.title: Kaateri
programme.desc: A group of treasure-seeking crooks travel to a mysterious hillside village looking for gold. However, nothing prepares them for what they witness there.

programme.title: Mirchi Masala
programme.desc: A woman decides to fight against her powerful oppressor. When the guard of a chilli factory helps her, the women and the teacher of the village join them to openly defy the prevailing repression.

programme.title: Cheranin Thirumanam
programme.desc: Mahesh and Aathira fall in love and tell their parents about their relationship. Though the families initially agree, they suddenly change their minds owing to the financial differences between them.

programme.title: Tarak Mehta Ka Chhota Chasma Ep21
programme.desc: Tarak Mehta Ka Chhota Chasma

programme.title: Hagola Ep25
programme.desc: A conversational comedy, set in the northern heartlands of India, transports kids into the world of three crazy friends - Hathgola, Goli and Lattha

programme.title: Hagola Ep26
programme.desc: A conversational comedy, set in the northern heartlands of India, transports kids into the world of three crazy friends - Hathgola, Goli and Lattha

programme.title: Guru Aur Bhole Ep4
programme.desc: Guru’s onomatopoeic singing talents adds to Bhole’s unique dancing style and brute strength which helps them to get out of many sticky situations. First of it’s kind, an Animated musical comedy, this show brings together laughter, action and music.

programme.title: Guru Aur Bhole Ep5
